DestroyModuleConfig EventNameBrowser:*
*EventNameBrowser: Cmd Function
*EventNameBrowser: add_window BrowserSaveName
*EventNameBrowser: window_name BrowserChangeName
*EventNameBrowser: destroy_window BrowserDeleteName

DestroyFunc BrowserChangeName
AddToFunc   BrowserChangeName
+ I Echo BrowserChangeName $[w.id] $[w.iconname] $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]
+ I ThisWindow ("firefox") BrowserUseName
+ I ThisWindow ("Brave-browser") BrowserUseName
+ I ThisWindow ("Google-chrome") BrowserUseName

DestroyFunc BrowserUseName
AddToFunc   BrowserUseName
+ I Echo BrowserUseName $[w.id] $[w.iconname] $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]
#Make sure infostore has the info for this window
+ I Test (!EnvIsSet $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]) Break
+ I WindowStyle TitleFormat %c $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]
+ I WindowStyle IconTitleFormat %c $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]

DestroyFunc BrowserDeleteName
AddToFunc   BrowserDeleteName
+ I Echo BrowserDeleteName $[w.id] $[w.iconname] $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]
+ I InfoStoreRemove browsername-$[w.id] $[infostore.WHICHBROWSER]

DestroyFunc BrowserSaveName
AddToFunc   BrowserSaveName
+ I Echo BrowserSaveName $[w.id] $[w.iconname] $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]
+ I ThisWindow ("firefox") BrowserDoSave "firefox"
+ I ThisWindow ("Brave-browser") BrowserDoSave "brave"
+ I ThisWindow ("Google-chrome") BrowserDoSave "chrome"

DestroyFunc BrowserDoSave
AddToFunc   BrowserDoSave
+ I PipeRead '${HOME}/.fvwm/scripts/getlatestbrowsertype.py $0'
+ I Echo BrowserDoSave $[w.id] $[w.iconname] $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]] $[infostore.WHICHBROWSER]
+ I InfoStoreAdd browsername-$[w.id] $[infostore.WHICHBROWSER]
+ I WindowStyle TitleFormat %c $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]
+ I WindowStyle IconTitleFormat %c $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]

#firefox startup

DestroyFunc MoveWindowLoc
AddtoFunc MoveWindowLoc
+ I Echo MoveWindowLoc $0 $1 $2 $3 $4
+ I WindowId $0 MoveToDesk 0 $1
+ I WindowId $0 MoveToPage $2 $3
+ I WindowId $0 MoveToScreen $4
+ I Schedule 200 GotoDesk 0 $1

#todo: when starting firefox: start program, sleep until it moves itself, reposition window to here
DestroyFunc Forcewindowhere
AddtoFunc Forcewindowhere
+ I Schedule 800 MoveWindowLoc $[w.id] $[desk.n] $[page.nx] $[page.ny] $[monitor.current]

Style firefox InitialMapCommand Forcewindowhere
